Part 8

results<-data.frame(estimate.ability=rep(NA,1000), std.err.ability=rep(NA, 1000),
                    estimate.score=rep(NA,1000), std.err.score=rep(NA, 1000))
results
for (i in c(1:1000)){
  
  mathsability<-rnorm(n=1000, mean=10, sd=2)
  
  mydataframe<-data.frame(id=c(1:1000), mathsability)
  
  otherfactors<-rnorm(n=1000, mean=0, sd=100)
  mydataframe$otherfactors<-otherfactors
  
  mydataframe$wage<-400+50*mydataframe$mathsability+mydataframe$otherfactors
  
  mydataframe$measurementerror<-rnorm(n=1000, mean=0, sd=0.5)
  
  mydataframe$obsscore<-mydataframe$mathsability+mydataframe$measurementerror
   
  regr1<-lm(data=mydataframe, wage~mathsability)
  summary(regr1)
  
  regr2<-lm(data=mydataframe, wage~obsscore)
  summary(regr2)
  
  library(broom)
  regrtable1<-tidy(regr1)
  regrtable2<-tidy(regr2)

  regrtable<-rbind(regrtable1,regrtable2)
  
  beta.ability<-regrtable$estimate[2]
  std.err.ability<-regrtable$std.error[2]
  beta.score<-regrtable$estimate[4]
  std.err.score<-regrtable$std.error[4]
  
  results$estimate.ability[i] <- beta.ability
  results$std.err.ability[i]<-std.err.ability
  results$estimate.score[i]<-beta.score
  results$std.err.score[i]<-std.err.score
  } 
results
